** Don't forget versioning! **

1. npm i typescript -g
 -- use `tsc --init` for tsconfig.json
 -- Uncomment...  "emitDecoratorMetadata": true,
                      "experimentalDecorators": true
  -- change "outDir": "./dist",
2. npm i routing-controllers -S
3. npm i reflect-metadata -S

4. and make sure to import it before you use routing-controllers:

import "reflect-metadata";

5. Install it with koa2 (it also supports express.js)

npm i koa koa-router koa-bodyparser koa-multer -S

6. Install koa types

npm i @types/koa @types/koa-router @types/koa-bodyparser -S

7. add `tsc` compiler to package.json

8. npm i nodemon -D && npm i ts-node -D
Nodemon + package.json + nodemon.json

9. Add userController.ts & app.ts

10. npm i typeorm -S && npm i mysql -S

11. ormconfig.json